Also, the USA pretty much has full support from nearly everyone on this if even one inspector is denied to take a crap in some super duper top secret bathroom. And believe me, they will be. They'll be wanting to drop a nice log in Saddams personal gold plated toilet - Any any hassle and they'll leave and Iraq will be forever changed.<br>
